<i>noun</i>: 추도 [추도], 추념 [추념] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>추도 [추도]</dt><br>
<dd>mourning; remembrance</dd><br>
<dd>죽은 사람을 생각하며 슬퍼함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of mourning, remembering a dead person.</dd><br>
<dt>추념 [추념]</dt><br>
<dd>1. remembrance; looking back on</dd><br>
<dd>지난 일을 생각함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of thinking about a past incident.</dd><br>
<dd>2. cherishing the memory of the deceased</dd><br>
<dd>죽은 사람을 생각함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of thinking about a dead person.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>